maintext:
Puzzles of the Past meeting set for May 10
GERING – Puzzles of the Past will be held Friday, May 10, at 9 a.m. Discussions will continue to focus on the town of Lyman.
This will be the last Puzzles of the Past meeting until September.
For more information, call Legacy of the Plains Museum at 308-436-1989.
